title: Plane crashed into a city bakery
text:
Plane crashed into a city bakery   
Oct 18, 2015 eTN   
A small plane with the identification HK-3917G and 4 passengers on board injured seven people after it crashed into a house in Engativá, part of Colombia’s capital.One person has been killed, according to local media reports 
Seven people have been sent to nearby hospitals, fire officials stated on Twitter. The plane landed on a bakery, affecting three nearby houses.
